    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By wrapping your hand around a small eyelike object, you become invisible until the spell ends. Anything you are wearing or carrying is invisible as long as it is on your person. The spell ends if you attack or cast another spell.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 1st level or higher, you can extend the duration by 1 round for each slot level (2 rounds at 1st and 3 rounds at 2nd).<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
